Wisdom is a minimalist Sinatra blog engine that loves Heroku.

Important! Wisdom is still alpha, use it for testing and not for production.

1) git clone git://github.com/zenati/wisdom.git
2) cd wisdom
3) heroku config --long (to retreive your Postgres username and password)
3) open app.rb and change your blog and database settings.
4) git add .
5) git commit -m "my new blog"
6) heroku create
7) git push heroku master
8) heroku open